{"tid":1001200,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[原創]想做插畫家","createTime":"2019-01-30T03:17:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T02:16:10.000Z","uid":152692,"like":245,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"ddcff7efa9ec915f6e02c0b720aa71b6b3256ae2","tid":1001200,"uid":152692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T03:17:06.000Z","msg":"我是一個90後，畢業後工作了三年多，宜家正職做緊工程師。雖然我冇設計/藝術的學歷，但平時都會在工餘/課餘時間畫畫。如果你問我理想是做什麼，其實我也不知道，但可能自己相對比較喜歡創作和創新，但好明顯這些都是在香港沒有價值的東西。其實，小時候我一直都希望可以創造一些獨一無異的東西，例如成為一個發明家去改變世界，但由於做產品的成本高，最後我只能選用最便宜的工具，就是紙和筆。然而，到了畢業後我沒有成為一個創業家，亦沒有成為一個插畫家，都係去咗打工。不過，我依然都會在工餘時間畫畫，雖然辛苦，但我也堅持住，即使到了今天，沒有任何收入以及知名度。<br />\n<br />\n和大部分香港現今的插畫不同，我不是主力做寫實派（雖然都會畫），也不太喜歡畫純粹呃like的漫畫，我比較著重創作意念和設計。不過，這可能在香港不會有太大的市場吧，而因為我的本科和藝術設計完全無關，加上屋企人也不支持我，所以我除了自己之外，似乎也沒有任何人脈可以幫到我。<br />\n<br />\n大概於上年年中開始，我創造了一系列的人物插畫，主要都係以香港的建築、風土人情為題材，用擬人化將它變成人物，進行二次創作，例如灣仔會展、尖沙咀鐘樓、大坑舞火龍丶鴨靈號等的角色。老實說，當初我設計這些人設的靈感來源是因為看到了艦娘/賽馬娘等的擬人創作，繼而嘗試利用香港文化來創造出有本地文化的角色，並制作一個遊戲，最後輾轉發展到今天。<br />\n<br />\n不過，值得慶幸的是，我早前參加了些資助計劃，並成功得到了政府的資助，金額雖然不多，但我也因此成立了公司，叫做踏出了第一步。Funding 唔會帶到我行得好遠，但至少我希望的是它能夠帶給我一些有用的network，由其是我呢類業餘人士。唔期望插畫會為我帶來咩收入，亦都未太唸到點發展下去。不過，可能暫時唯一可以做的事情，可能就是爭取些展覽的機會，以及尋找一些可能的合作。<br />\n<br />\n然而，始終一個人的能力是有限的，我現在除了要返正職，同時亦勉強算是一個插畫家和創業家，兼顧的東西很多。雖然辛苦，但既然開始左，就只有繼續走下去。但現階段應該沒有能力可以請一個fulltime去幫忙。開post除了希望找到些支持外，同時都希望可以找到些有心有力的人合作，尤其希望認識些制作遊戲/board game有經驗的人。謝謝。<br />\n<br />\n我的傳送門：<br />\nig: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/s19naturehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fs19naturehk&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfB8wxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=057b27e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/s19naturehk</a><br />\nfb: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/s19naturehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fs19naturehk&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfB8wxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=10a6b2a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/s19naturehk</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZeO6N7E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZeO6N7E.jpg&h=9a2833cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tcxZ76k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtcxZ76k.jpg&h=f796d048&s={SIZE}\" />[img][/img]<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WtEYEdm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWtEYEdm.jpg&h=f4f449f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o8AEoE2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo8AEoE2.jpg&h=ad55b2c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vUb4zMJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvUb4zMJ.jpg&h=79872d64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dqjYEdp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdqjYEdp.jpg&h=b377fbff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qv1DEdq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqv1DEdq.jpg&h=c834d8f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YpEReMM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYpEReMM.jpg&h=448ea4dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ahboQkg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FahboQkg.jpg&h=45171870&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wwuJQkn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwwuJQkn.jpg&h=d8142088&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BHr8g0q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBHr8g0q.jpg&h=35cf3ea5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FcQAGsj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFcQAGsj.jpg&h=1b8731f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5yV1B0N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5yV1B0N.jpg&h=f56144cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0fc2242302ff800fbe50696f9958146c32d5141e","tid":1001200,"uid":152692,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T03:18:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d56e79ce996cae77b4b13eeec510ee4690be7912","tid":1001200,"uid":129142,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T03:31:04.000Z","msg":"樓主畫功好勁 仲要上埋色咁有心機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係呢方面嘅專家 只可以幫你打個氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caa4d39b8a686a9f36979f6fe60ed07b338753f7","tid":1001200,"uid":152692,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"d56e79ce996cae77b4b13eeec510ee4690be7912","tid":1001200,"uid":129142,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T03:31:04.000Z","msg":"樓主畫功好勁 仲要上埋色咁有心機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係呢方面嘅專家 只可以幫你打個氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T03:35:18.000Z","msg":"香港越來越少人有心機了，我都係趁我自己仲有心機，再睇下有冇D有心機嘅、有能力的人去合作下。呢D都係我宜家唯一可以做的事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e1e922e140d4e4c33686d10020c945249b006a2","tid":1001200,"uid":86833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T03:36:19.000Z","msg":"G持"},{"pid":"39b026134ededcea806559a91d3de1ae31413349","tid":1001200,"uid":199331,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T03:43:15.000Z","msg":"推，利申都係工程畫畫撚"},{"pid":"7dad89573bf21e39e983220eee38d1c3fe3c47f8","tid":1001200,"uid":46933,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T03:51:16.000Z","msg":"香港地<br />\n要多字先做到插畫家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bcf8c5a06c7991e81bf869e1d29a0a03c8546e5","tid":1001200,"uid":152692,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T03:56:10.000Z","msg":"老實講出下post都係算睇下不同人意見。百貨應百客，比如有好多人唔鍾意某D野，咪去了解下，或者有D人鍾意某方面，咪又去了解下。<br />\n<br />\n始終我自己冇可能一個人做到D咩product出來，例如一隻遊戲或者boardgame出來，冇時間、冇能力、亦都冇經驗。但我唸呢度點都會有D高手，唯一可以做都係睇下有冇人指教下。"},{"pid":"99f15e7da508293bc27ad04cc2183c21a7105280","tid":1001200,"uid":169779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T04:08:16.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"97fde13c3e0f14496c49d70b2d88200cbf1a8fda","tid":1001200,"uid":48319,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T04:23:38.000Z","msg":"搵個畫家做老婆"},{"pid":"388f7a42ebb91331b7d3c0be4c47122d3b018981","tid":1001200,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T04:24:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38fccb0aeffb87d960f74abd0a0ea39c575ffc83","tid":1001200,"uid":144611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T04:26:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40e3c0387c0f2310830b2ba2767d6fd558b9b4e6","tid":1001200,"uid":55855,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T04:28:36.000Z","msg":"我都係工程畫畫撚<br />\n支持樓主，我依家都練緊畫<br />\n希望可以快啲趕上樓主"},{"pid":"8ccd1110ecfcd30dbff4b4fd829f69a55e5a9a99","tid":1001200,"uid":152692,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"40e3c0387c0f2310830b2ba2767d6fd558b9b4e6","tid":1001200,"uid":55855,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T04:28:36.000Z","msg":"我都係工程畫畫撚<br />\n支持樓主，我依家都練緊畫<br />\n希望可以快啲趕上樓主"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T05:42:03.000Z","msg":"我都會繼續努力，唔比你超越。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過其實我宜家level都見得會有咩收入，即使再繼續發展落去未必有咩成果。你反而要睇可能係呢樣。"},{"pid":"3f2f845396d8d7f06ed9f9b346582c63fd82d3e1","tid":1001200,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T05:44:01.000Z","msg":"靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/