"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T02:22:54.000Z","msg":"冇錯，其實都係想走多少少設計嘅路線，但當然實力就未可以同頂尖果D比。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n畫CG呢類型係技術上的要求較高，所以練習和付出要較多，投資回本期極長。難聽講句，香港人係普遍要求回本期短、回報率高，呢D回本期慢嘅野自然越來越少人去做。相比下快餐回報可能會快少少，但當快餐個市場開始犯濫時，可能我再去做都冇乜意思。<br />\n<br />\n不過我唸做藝術同做生意有少少唔同，除了考慮錢同市場之外，另外一樣是面對自己本身。"},{"pid":"b4bcf72bb0c4f829757afc8cca51e428f19118f9","tid":1001200,"uid":233864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T02:34:29.000Z","msg":"G持樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac75f4353ddcccac4036d4745b8b905645da2641","tid":1001200,"uid":223583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T02:37:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> G持"},{"pid":"54c8054682af2add12707aad250c7c7594090f91","tid":1001200,"uid":173480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T02:50:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f155c26138bcd7d4e448148be7568f8e0b7844a","tid":1001200,"uid":220985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T03:00:45.000Z","msg":"我都冇相關學歷 程度都好一般 g 持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2449d00c282ea5ec69a768d667d405c3f19473a7","tid":1001200,"uid":220985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f155c26138bcd7d4e448148be7568f8e0b7844a","tid":1001200,"uid":2