ets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw,發現寫實風人像畫好難畫，風景更加係....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dceca29ff69dce816d9d1db9de870b93673a92eb","tid":1001200,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T07:22:12.000Z","msg":"你條女係畫家？"},{"pid":"07bb00e95c28d71978a74fd37d7f47565702b1c8","tid":1001200,"uid":23023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T07:26:22.000Z","msg":"樓主好有創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港地畫畫唔係咁易<br />\n有心keep到畫畫已經好勁<br />\n不過要搵食係香港就難好多<br />\n始終市場唔夠大<br />\n國際市場又唔一定要你<br />\n台灣日本市場比香港大得多<br />\n風氣都好好多<br />\n<br />\nBtw 樓主畫得太平面<br />\n人物冇咩立體感覺<br />\n建議修練一下line of action<br />\n同埋睇一睇人體基本結構"},{"pid":"f3e355b4fbbc41b3ff13cd2a53dbd7c3c0402c26","tid":1001200,"uid":152692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"07bb00e95c28d71978a74fd37d7f47565702b1c8","tid":1001200,"uid":23023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T07:26:22.000Z","msg":"樓主好有創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港地畫畫唔係咁易<br />\n有心keep到畫畫已經好勁<br />\n不過要搵食係香港就難好多<br />\n始終市場唔夠大<br />\n國際市場又唔一定要你<br />\n台灣日本市場比香港大得多<br />\n風氣都好好多<br />\n<br />\nBtw 樓主畫得太平面<br />\n人物冇咩立體感覺<br />\n建議修練一下line of action<br />\n同埋睇一睇人體基本結構"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:12:31.000Z","msg":"畫功果方面永遠都要繼續去練。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外如果講市場、受眾性，尤其係講香港文化...老實講本身從一開始都唔太expect香港人會好buy。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為會對香港文化有興趣嘅人反而係外地人。<br />\n<br />\n其實boardgame或者係文字遊戲，都有佢哋嘅市場。但多數係會target外地為主，而唔會係香港。"},{"pid":"eab9ea651d8f75e9826e6848e1f5a928b8d8c18b","tid":1001200,"uid":129712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-3